metadata.name: Space Traveler #1
metadata.description:
Travelers are Universal beings of love and light. They represent a unified field of consciousness where time and space are infinite. Travelers are here to spread messages of Love, unity and collective consciousness. We are the Universe, we are one.

All 1/1 Travelers in this collection are hand-drawn digitally on Procreate. 

Original artwork by Sarkis Delimelkon.
SARKISM
